snippet.title: Welcome Nakayoshi Park, Game Boy Longplay
snippet.description:
Played by: Black Fire (~Alexandr 日本語)

Welcome Nakayoshi Park is a video game released in 1994 by Bandai for the Nintendo Game Boy. It featured several characters from different manga series published in Nakayoshi magazine, including Sailor Moon characters. 

In the game, the player walks around Nakayoshi park, playing different mini-games. After they are all beaten, the player can gain access to a castle in the center of the park. This game features several other characters from Nakayoshi magazine along with Sailor Moon characters.
